{"tid":1360813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加、愛兩國對港發出旅遊警示","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:07:03.000Z","uid":134134,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4c01900897fd40fe4bc10fad4d37d1958cfe06","tid":1360813,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"《愛爾蘭提升港旅遊警示至高度警戒　加國促避去示威地點》<br />\n<br />\n因應本港近期接連出現示威衝突，愛爾蘭外交貿易部對港澳地區發出旅遊警示，並將旅遊安全級別提升至「高度警戒」級別。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭當局指，個別示威者與警方衝突，警方要以催淚彈及橡膠子彈等維持秩序，在未來日子示威可能持續，建議愛爾蘭民眾避免前往出現示威或無預告公眾集會的地區，特別是金鐘一帶。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大亦更新了對本港的外遊警示，指由上月初起金鐘、維園等地區，以至九龍及新界郊區出現大型示威，可能持續、影響交通，建議加拿大公民避免到示威或大型集會地方。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：RTHK即時新聞<br />\n2019-07-24 19:33:53"},{"pid":"e39ebd46ba4ef175f53a042179220b99c20efb10","tid":1360813,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db8ee2115aa870c3229b4463e3b0fce4fecb16e","tid":1360813,"uid":62133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"避免去示威地點<br />\n咁如果係景點示威呢？"},{"pid":"a34cb6c7dbb0387a287ef556c4dd0cea5c5fe66d","tid":1360813,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5db8ee2115aa870c3229b4463e3b0fce4fecb16e","tid":1360813,"uid":62133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"避免去示威地點<br />\n咁如果係景點示威呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}